<section class="partners">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2>Partners Tecnológicos</h2>
            <p>Empresas líderes en su sector que cumplen con los estándares de fiabilidad y solidez establecida por nuestra entidad.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="partners-logo-grid">
            <img src="g400-logo.png" alt="Partner 1" class="partner-logo">
            <img src="g400-logo.png" alt="Partner 2" class="partner-logo">
            <img src="g400-logo.png" alt="IBM" class="partner-logo">
            <img src="g400-logo.png" alt="Partner 4" class="partner-logo">
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<style>

    
/* ==========================================================================
   11. PARTNERS SECTION
   ========================================================================== */

.partners {
    padding: 120px 0;
    background-color: var(--light);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
}

.partners::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 500px;
    height: 500px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 69, 255, 0.05) 0%, rgba(0, 240, 255, 0) 70%);
    top: -250px;
    right: -250px;
}

.partners::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 500px;
    height: 500px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 0, 132, 0.05) 0%, rgba(0, 240, 255, 0) 70%);
    bottom: -250px;
    left: -250px;
}

.partners-logo-grid {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 70px;
    margin-top: 70px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
}

.partner-logo {
    height: 80px;
    filter: grayscale(100%) brightness(0.9);
    opacity: 0.6;
    transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.19, 1, 0.22, 1);
    transform-origin: center;
    position: relative;
}

.partner-logo:hover {
    filter: grayscale(0%) brightness(1);
    opacity: 1;
    transform: scale(1.2);
}

.partner-logo::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    left: -50%;
    width: 200%;
    height: 200%;
    background: linear-gradient(
        to right,
        rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 0%,
        rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3) 50%,
        rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 100%
    );
    transform: rotate(30deg);
    transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.19, 1, 0.22, 1);
    opacity: 0;
}

.partner-logo:hover::after {
    animation: shineEffect 1s forwards;
}

</style>